<br>
Don't believe that?  Here's a simple test: compare a group without a slower -v- a group without a tank.  I'm sure most people know that the group without a tank will find the slower tanking most mobs.<br>
<br>
Well, the thing is that your cleric will use <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>a lot</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> less mana healing the group without a tank than they would healing the group without a slower.  I know, I've done both enough times to say this for sure.<br>
<br>
From this follows the basic principle:  Slow on inc, all the time, every time.  It's always cheaper to heal the chanter who's tanking a slowed mob than to heal the warrior who's tanking it unslowed.  Always.  So giving your tank &quot;time to build aggro&quot; is stupid. <p>_________________<br>
Shadowfrost<br>
Justified Ancient of Mu Mu</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=1154.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=1154.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=1154.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=1154.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=1154.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=1154.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=1154.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=1154.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1154.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=1154.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.threadControl?topicID=1154.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1154.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultima